			Profile
			
			YunPan(赟潘)
HereceivedhisB.S.degreeinDepartmentofInformationScience&amp;ElectronicEngineering,ZhejiangUniversityin2002,andPh.DdegreeinElectronicEngineering,TsinghuaUniversityin2008,supervisedbyProf.ZaiwangDongandProf.NingGe.&nbsp;HejoinedInstituteofVLSIDesign,CollegeofElectricalEngineering,ZhejiangUniversityin2008asapostdoctorsupervisedbyProf.XiaolangYan.&nbsp;HevisitedProf.LucClaesen'sresearchgroupatUniversityHasselt,BelgiumfromJulytoAugustin2013.FromNovember2013tonow,heisdoinghisresearchinthelabofProf.Kwang-Ting(Tim)ChengatUniversityofCalifornia,SantaBarbara,U.S.asavisitingassociateresearcher.
&nbsp;
HeiscurrentlyafacultymemberofDepartmentofInformationScience&amp;ElectronicEngineering,ZhejiangUniversityasanAssociateProfessorandPh.D.advisor.Hiscurrentresearchinterestsincludeon-chipcommunicationandnetwork-on-chip,mobileembeddedsystemsandmobilehealthcare(ECGsensor),heterogeneousarchitecturedesignsforapplication-specificalgorithms,architecturedesignforparticlefilters,smartcamerasystems,circuitdesignforsoftware-definedradio.Hehaspublishedmorethan40academicpapers,coauthored2books,andheldover&nbsp;8Chinesepatentsintheseareas.
